Answer: Performance and stress testing on staging servers before release to production to prevent possible issues. For tracking production activities can be used Android profiler.
• How would you debug issues related to API usage? Can you give us an example?
Answer: I have used Postman for API issues debug process. Example: selecting items in specified time period, pagination.
